523
00:25:11.633 --> 00:25:15.799
with allergies and she's had pneumonia a couple of times

524
00:25:15.799 --> 00:25:18.969
and asthma

525
00:25:18.969 --> 00:25:21.004
just everything you can name.

526
00:25:21.004 --> 00:25:23.703
<v ->The last two years she's</v>

527
00:25:23.703 --> 00:25:26.742
seemed to have gotten worse as far as the fatigue goes

528
00:25:26.742 --> 00:25:29.169
and was actually on Homebound through school

529
00:25:29.169 --> 00:25:33.489
she couldn't even make it at school.

530
00:25:33.489 --> 00:25:36.626
And this lasted for about a year and a half

531
00:25:36.626 --> 00:25:39.322
she would be sick with bronchitis

532
00:25:39.322 --> 00:25:40.924
she'd be well for about a week or so,

533
00:25:40.924 --> 00:25:43.059
not well but she wouldn't have the bronchitis

534
00:25:43.059 --> 00:25:45.605
so she would still be extremely tired.

535
00:25:45.605 --> 00:25:49.059
<v ->And I called George into her room</v>

536
00:25:49.059 --> 00:25:51.718
and we just sat and talked for awhile

537
00:25:51.718 --> 00:25:56.005
just to get her comfortable with him

538
00:25:56.005 --> 00:26:00.552
and George said, tell her to put her hand beside her.

539
00:26:02.512 --> 00:26:07.251
And she did, and he put his hand on hers

540
00:26:07.251 --> 00:26:09.886
and I said let's just pray and we did.

541
00:26:09.886 --> 00:26:11.905
<v ->Sarah told me everything he was gonna do</v>

542
00:26:11.905 --> 00:26:14.490
and to just relax and he did it

543
00:26:14.490 --> 00:26:17.694
and he just you know put his hand on me

544
00:26:17.694 --> 00:26:20.564
and I don't know what he did or what he said

545
00:26:20.564 --> 00:26:23.466
or how he did it but you know

546
00:26:23.466 --> 00:26:24.701
all I know is, he put his hand on me

547
00:26:24.701 --> 00:26:28.287
and then it became

548
00:26:28.287 --> 00:26:31.127
better very quickly.

549
00:26:31.127 --> 00:26:32.085
<v Voiceover>The Homebound teachers</v>

