00:26:32.085 --> 00:26:34.816
that had worked with her was just like well...

551
00:26:34.816 --> 00:26:36.947
especially one in particular, Myra

552
00:26:36.947 --> 00:26:39.526
she had tears in her eyes and just was,

553
00:26:39.526 --> 00:26:42.522
What? What happened? I mean you know, this is just wonderful

554
00:26:42.522 --> 00:26:45.155
she's doing so great and I could just look at her

555
00:26:45.155 --> 00:26:47.657
with tears in my eyes and say it's been a miracle

556
00:26:47.657 --> 00:26:49.243
because it has been,

557
00:26:49.243 --> 00:26:53.413
it's been an incredible miracle.

558
00:26:53.413 --> 00:26:56.178
<v Voiceover>When Sarah was fully recovered</v>

