00:27:06.046 --> 00:27:07.644
I said okay, I will.

564
00:27:07.644 --> 00:27:10.504
And I thought we were gonna play a game,

565
00:27:10.504 --> 00:27:13.316
and so I went into another room

566
00:27:13.316 --> 00:27:14.417
brought my paper and pencil

