00:27:14.417 --> 00:27:18.855
and he told me to write down everything that he said.

568
00:27:18.855 --> 00:27:20.554
"You must see that everyone within your reach

569
00:27:20.554 --> 00:27:23.510
"hears about what happened to you, all of it,

570
00:27:23.510 --> 00:27:26.447
"you must open their eyes and give them hope.

571
00:27:26.447 --> 00:27:27.987
"Dedicate your soul to healing people

572
00:27:27.987 --> 00:27:31.519
"simply by talking and letting everyone know

573
00:27:31.519 --> 00:27:34.498
"how the world is changing.

574
00:27:34.498 --> 00:27:36.777
"You'll begin to get responses,

575
00:27:36.777 --> 00:27:39.769
"ideas will come, solutions to problems will appear

576
00:27:39.769 --> 00:27:41.772
"and the people will send you letters suggesting

577
00:27:41.772 --> 00:27:43.780
"and supporting you.

578
00:27:43.780 --> 00:27:46.320
"Some people will be negative but these are the people

579
00:27:46.320 --> 00:27:48.118
"that are harder to reach.

580
00:27:48.118 --> 00:27:50.853
"Don't let them discourage you.

581
00:27:50.853 --> 00:27:54.493
"You have proven to be strong and your family as well.

582
00:27:54.493 --> 00:27:56.726
"I know you can get through this

583
00:27:56.726 --> 00:27:58.998
"and when you do,

584
00:27:58.998 --> 00:28:02.866
"you'll come out even more strong than before.

585
00:28:02.866 --> 00:28:04.234
"You're the mouth that they will hear

586
00:28:04.234 --> 00:28:07.705
"because you are a child... a child of God

587
00:28:07.705 --> 00:28:11.958
"and a child who can bring hope to God's people.

588
00:28:11.958 --> 00:28:15.294
"Please stay peaceful and one with God."

589
00:28:17.484 --> 00:28:18.996
<v ->I have to thank him,</v>

590
00:28:18.996 --> 00:28:22.999
as I have to thank God,

591
00:28:22.999 --> 00:28:25.708
that he...

592
00:28:25.708 --> 00:28:28.028
did for Sarah

593
00:28:28.028 --> 00:28:31.228
so many things that for a time

594
00:28:31.228 --> 00:28:33.596
I could not do.

595
00:28:33.596 --> 00:28:35.499
<v ->And she told me George was gone</v>

596
00:28:35.499 --> 00:28:39.035
and I was, it was like a death

597
00:28:39.035 --> 00:28:41.952
of someone in the immediate family

598
00:28:41.952 --> 00:28:45.802
it was like a death of somebody that I had been

599
00:28:45.802 --> 00:28:48.138
close to all my life.

600
00:28:48.138 --> 00:28:49.498
And I didn't know whether I was

601
00:28:49.498 --> 00:28:51.885
feeling all the pain for Sarah

602
00:28:51.885 --> 00:28:55.812
and thinking how she must feel, just devastated.

603
00:28:55.812 --> 00:29:00.690
And, or whether it was just my own, you know, self

604
00:29:00.690 --> 00:29:04.334
missing his presence and knowing that

605
00:29:04.334 --> 00:29:07.547
he wouldn't be around the same way anymore.

606
00:29:07.547 --> 00:29:10.660
<v ->I think everybody has their own personal</v>

607
00:29:10.660 --> 00:29:12.003
guardian angel.

608
00:29:12.003 --> 00:29:13.640
And it's really amazing to think that there's

609
00:29:13.640 --> 00:29:14.771
somebody just for me

610
00:29:14.771 --> 00:29:17.541
somebody that God sent just for me.

611
00:29:19.431 --> 00:29:23.013
That's what I always think if I ever fell down.

612
00:29:23.013 --> 00:29:24.957
<v Voiceover>A noticeable side effect in those</v>

613
00:29:24.957 --> 00:29:28.017
whose lives have been touched by an angel

614
00:29:28.017 --> 00:29:31.682
is a profound change in their sense of priorities.

615
00:29:33.802 --> 00:29:36.260
<v ->I just feel like Sarah's had a glimpse</v>

616
00:29:36.260 --> 00:29:38.762
of something the rest of us haven't

617
00:29:38.762 --> 00:29:40.830
and so it's changed the way she

618
00:29:40.830 --> 00:29:45.478
looks at everything and everybody.

619
00:29:45.478 --> 00:29:49.072
She sees what's really important.

620
00:29:49.072 --> 00:29:51.511
<v ->Faith is the one thing that people should have</v>

621
00:29:51.511 --> 00:29:54.717
and you can't just

622
00:29:54.717 --> 00:29:57.042
get faith by seeing something and then believing it.

623
00:29:57.042 --> 00:29:59.581
You have to

624
00:30:02.121 --> 00:30:03.687
You have to have doubts first

625
00:30:03.687 --> 00:30:04.921
and then come through

626
00:30:04.921 --> 00:30:08.551
and you have to learn by other things and...

627
00:30:12.071 --> 00:30:16.567
Trust is another part of faith.

628
00:30:16.567 --> 00:30:17.440
Just like the Bible,

629
00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:20.236
you have to believe, you have to believe the Word of God,

630
00:30:20.236 --> 00:30:21.538
you can't go up to 'em and say

631
00:30:21.538 --> 00:30:22.472
well how do I know this is true?

632
00:30:22.472 --> 00:30:23.906
What are you gonna give me?

633
00:30:23.906 --> 00:30:26.642
What are you gonna show me?

