00:31:51.394 --> 00:31:54.106
and immorality and then that went into

668
00:31:54.106 --> 00:31:56.633
a culture of the "Me generation"

669
00:31:56.633 --> 00:31:58.501
and then that kind of went into a culture of

670
00:31:58.501 --> 00:32:01.320
materialism and acquiring things

671
00:32:01.320 --> 00:32:03.339
and through all of this our hearts

672
00:32:03.339 --> 00:32:05.905
have become more and more empty.

673
00:32:05.905 --> 00:32:08.377
That God-shaped hole that we've tried to fill

674
00:32:08.377 --> 00:32:10.747
with all these other things has become

675
00:32:10.747 --> 00:32:12.565
more and more wounded.

676
00:32:12.565 --> 00:32:14.016
<v ->It's really no accident that materialism</v>

677
00:32:14.016 --> 00:32:15.852
is on the wane.

678
00:32:15.852 --> 00:32:17.086
That the leading thinkers,

