00:32:47.571 --> 00:32:49.015
You have the Gaia hypothesis

694
00:32:49.015 --> 00:32:52.666
which indicates that the very planet that we live on

695
00:32:52.666 --> 00:32:55.358
and all of its' functioning systems that keep us alive

696
00:32:55.358 --> 00:32:58.562
are here against incredible odds.

697
00:32:58.562 --> 00:33:00.197
You have quantum physics

698
00:33:00.197 --> 00:33:03.399
which shows us that our basic reality

699
00:33:03.399 --> 00:33:05.268
the reality that our world is based on

700
00:33:05.268 --> 00:33:07.057
down there at that little sub-atomic level

701
00:33:07.057 --> 00:33:08.905
is a never never land

702
00:33:08.905 --> 00:33:13.443
a place where consciousness shapes reality and determines it

703
00:33:13.443 --> 00:33:15.882
where reality is not where matter is not

704
00:33:15.882 --> 00:33:19.586
supreme indeed, matter in a very real sense

705
00:33:19.586 --> 00:33:22.615
has no existence apart from consciousness

706
00:33:22.615 --> 00:33:25.455
apart from the observer looking at it.

