00:34:03.496 --> 00:34:07.797
in your arteries and you have an aneurysm in the aorta.

722
00:34:07.797 --> 00:34:09.599
And he said, you're not to leave the hospital until

723
00:34:09.599 --> 00:34:13.136
we have surgery.

724
00:34:13.136 --> 00:34:15.921
The surgery didn't go as well as expected.

725
00:34:15.921 --> 00:34:17.908
I was supposed to be out in three to five days

