00:34:17.908 --> 00:34:20.616
and I saw three roommates had passed through

727
00:34:20.616 --> 00:34:23.279
my room before I was able to leave.

728
00:34:23.279 --> 00:34:26.149
And I continued to have problems.

729
00:34:26.149 --> 00:34:30.354
Blood clots and a feeling of total disorientation

730
00:34:30.354 --> 00:34:33.523
and I just, things weren't right.

731
00:34:33.523 --> 00:34:35.054
Doctors said we're gonna have to keep testing

732
00:34:35.054 --> 00:34:36.800
and find out what's wrong.

733
00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:38.417
Over the next 18 months,

734
00:34:38.417 --> 00:34:42.265
I had six surgeries and I didn't feel

735
00:34:42.265 --> 00:34:44.534
like I was ever going to leave that hospital

736
00:34:44.534 --> 00:34:48.171
I felt that

737
00:34:48.171 --> 00:34:51.000
this was gonna be the termination

738
00:34:51.000 --> 00:34:55.313
of my ministry, termination of my life.

