00:34:55.313 --> 00:34:58.548
And, the doctor came in

740
00:34:58.548 --> 00:35:00.950
and he said,

741
00:35:00.950 --> 00:35:03.706
we've done all we can do.

742
00:35:03.706 --> 00:35:06.789
That, there's nothing more we can do

