00:35:06.789 --> 00:35:09.058
but turn it over to your body

744
00:35:09.058 --> 00:35:12.328
and let your body work on it.

745
00:35:12.328 --> 00:35:16.132
I wasn't comfortable with that and so I

746
00:35:16.132 --> 00:35:19.636
I started praying... the room got very quiet

747
00:35:19.636 --> 00:35:21.718
very still

748
00:35:21.718 --> 00:35:23.774
and the head nurse came in.

749
00:35:23.774 --> 00:35:26.342
She had been in to see me

750
00:35:26.342 --> 00:35:29.585
every 15 to 20 minutes

751
00:35:29.585 --> 00:35:34.194
and she stood alongside of me

752
00:35:34.194 --> 00:35:37.617
and she said, I could remember her words so clearly.

753
00:35:37.617 --> 00:35:40.890
She said, just relax

754
00:35:40.890 --> 00:35:44.647
She said, I know everything will be all right.

755
00:35:44.647 --> 00:35:48.545
And she put her hand on my right arm

756
00:35:48.545 --> 00:35:50.766
and began to stroke it

757
00:35:50.766 --> 00:35:54.740
and she said, you will be okay.

758
00:35:54.740 --> 00:35:59.275
We're in control of what's happening to you.

759
00:35:59.275 --> 00:36:02.345
And I began to feel warm

760
00:36:02.345 --> 00:36:06.929
a sense of wholeness came over me.

761
00:36:06.929 --> 00:36:09.520
And I didn't hear any other voices

762
00:36:09.520 --> 00:36:11.921
other than hers, was saying and reassuring me

763
00:36:11.921 --> 00:36:15.292
that everything was gonna be all right.

764
00:36:15.292 --> 00:36:18.294
And after a period of I don't know how long

765
00:36:18.294 --> 00:36:19.633
it was a very short time

766
00:36:19.633 --> 00:36:23.149
she said I'm gonna go call the doctor.

767
00:36:23.149 --> 00:36:25.201
I want the doctor to come in and look at you

768
00:36:25.201 --> 00:36:27.169
and so the doctor came in and

769
00:36:27.169 --> 00:36:29.839
and he said, I don't know what's happened

770
00:36:29.839 --> 00:36:33.842
but, he said, you've made a sudden turn.

771
00:36:33.842 --> 00:36:38.782
And he said, I think you've passed the crisis.

772
00:36:38.782 --> 00:36:43.156
And I said, well, I knew that too.

773
00:36:43.156 --> 00:36:45.644
And he said, how did you know that?

774
00:36:45.644 --> 00:36:50.492
And I said, because the angel touched me.

775
00:36:50.492 --> 00:36:53.162
And he laughed and he said, what do you mean?

776
00:36:53.162 --> 00:36:54.001
And I said, no,

777
00:36:54.001 --> 00:36:57.700
the angel who was present in my room touched me

778
00:36:57.700 --> 00:37:00.169
and that made all the difference.

779
00:37:00.169 --> 00:37:03.439
It was the nurse who had touched me.

780
00:37:03.439 --> 00:37:07.576
And after I began to feel stronger, she

781
00:37:07.576 --> 00:37:10.613
I told her what had happened

782
00:37:10.613 --> 00:37:13.116
and she said, you mean you thought I was an angel?

783
00:37:13.116 --> 00:37:14.617
And I said, no,

784
00:37:14.617 --> 00:37:18.277
I knew you were an angel.

785
00:37:18.277 --> 00:37:21.631
And that God was working through you

786
00:37:21.631 --> 00:37:25.895
to bring me back from wherever I was headed.

787
00:37:25.895 --> 00:37:28.531
And she was kind of overwhelmed by it all

788
00:37:28.531 --> 00:37:32.405
and she said, I've never had this experience before.

789
00:37:32.405 --> 00:37:34.804
And I said, well I can assure you I never have either.

790
00:37:34.804 --> 00:37:37.450
(laughs)

791
00:37:37.450 --> 00:37:40.142
But I said, I believe very strongly that

792
00:37:40.142 --> 00:37:43.658
you were God's angel for me

793
00:37:43.658 --> 00:37:45.638
and I will forever thank you,

794
00:37:45.638 --> 00:37:48.323
for what you've done.

795
00:37:53.757 --> 00:37:55.509
<v Voiceover>An angel speaks,</v>

796
00:37:55.509 --> 00:37:59.829
a human listens and responds

797
00:37:59.829 --> 00:38:02.665
maybe we should all learn to listen more carefully

798
00:38:02.665 --> 00:38:05.569
to these messengers of God.

799
00:38:05.569 --> 00:38:08.837
But what about those other messages?

800
00:38:08.837 --> 00:38:13.436
Those sudden inclinations to do something bad?

801
00:38:13.436 --> 00:38:15.978
We can't escape the truth

802
00:38:15.978 --> 00:38:18.647
the presence of evil seems to be alive and well

803
00:38:18.647 --> 00:38:21.634
across the face of the earth.

804
00:38:21.634 --> 00:38:25.572
Just where are the good angels in all of this?

805
00:38:25.572 --> 00:38:28.525
<v ->People wonder if there are indeed angels</v>

806
00:38:28.525 --> 00:38:33.162
who are here protecting us why then do we have

807
00:38:33.162 --> 00:38:37.700
such..such things as children who starve to death

808
00:38:37.700 --> 00:38:39.536
and events like the Holocaust

809
00:38:39.536 --> 00:38:41.638
how could these things happen when angels are

810
00:38:41.638 --> 00:38:45.274
supposed to protect us and to watch over us?

811
00:38:45.274 --> 00:38:49.331
I'd like to remind us of something very simple

812
00:38:49.331 --> 00:38:53.315
and that that is that this is an evil that human beings

813
00:38:53.315 --> 00:38:56.320
inflict upon one another.

814
00:38:56.320 --> 00:38:59.389
<v ->So I guess when we ask that kind of a question</v>

815
00:38:59.389 --> 00:39:01.290
what we're doing in a sense is we're making

816
00:39:01.290 --> 00:39:03.342
a judgement about God.

817
00:39:03.342 --> 00:39:04.626
You know, what kind of a God

818
00:39:04.626 --> 00:39:07.096
would permit this kind of thing to happen?

819
00:39:07.096 --> 00:39:08.564
And in this case you're asking also

820
00:39:08.564 --> 00:39:10.265
the question about angels.

821
00:39:10.265 --> 00:39:12.768
How could angels permit this to be?

822
00:39:12.768 --> 00:39:16.039
And yet, I wonder if in the long run

823
00:39:16.039 --> 00:39:17.973
we ourselves as humans will not also

824
00:39:17.973 --> 00:39:20.149
have to face that same judgement.

825
00:39:20.149 --> 00:39:23.225
How could we as human beings let these kinds of things

826
00:39:23.225 --> 00:39:24.913
be happening in our world.

827
00:39:24.913 --> 00:39:26.949
<v ->What if nothing bad ever happened?</v>

828
00:39:26.949 --> 00:39:29.518
What if everything was perfect?

829
00:39:29.518 --> 00:39:34.491
There was never any bad people no negativity

830
00:39:34.491 --> 00:39:38.928
Everybody had just enough money no crimes happened,

831
00:39:38.928 --> 00:39:39.942
everything would be handed to

832
00:39:39.942 --> 00:39:42.165
you wouldn't learn anything.

833
00:39:42.165 --> 00:39:43.566
Nobody would learn anything,

834
00:39:43.566 --> 00:39:45.701
you wouldn't have to work for anything.

835
00:39:45.701 --> 00:39:47.870
And I believe that that's why we're here is just

836
00:39:47.870 --> 00:39:49.478
simply a stopping point

837
00:39:49.478 --> 00:39:53.009
for a school if you will

838
00:39:53.009 --> 00:39:57.146
and sometimes bad things have to happen

839
00:39:57.146 --> 00:40:00.379
but there will... something good will come out of that.

840
00:40:00.379 --> 00:40:03.185
<v ->We are here to love one another</v>

841
00:40:03.185 --> 00:40:06.622
and to learn the ways of peace.

842
00:40:06.622 --> 00:40:10.459
If God were to intervene directly

843
00:40:10.459 --> 00:40:13.229
say to directly send an angel to put

844
00:40:13.229 --> 00:40:17.317
food into a child's mouth that is

845
00:40:17.317 --> 00:40:20.569
not teaching us that we have a responsibility

846
00:40:20.569 --> 00:40:23.105
to that child, if that child is to be fed

847
00:40:23.105 --> 00:40:25.208
it's to come from our hands.

848
00:40:25.208 --> 00:40:27.676
<v Voiceover>Angels don't want the attention on them.</v>

849
00:40:27.676 --> 00:40:30.079
They want us focused beyond them

850
00:40:30.079 --> 00:40:32.282
their pointing to heaven

851
00:40:32.282 --> 00:40:33.783
and they're disappearing, they're saying,

852
00:40:33.783 --> 00:40:35.817
that's where the peace is coming from,

853
00:40:35.817 --> 00:40:38.024
that's where you have to start.

854
00:40:38.024 --> 00:40:39.888
So you've got to put God back

855
00:40:39.888 --> 00:40:42.124
and then everything else will make sense

856
00:40:42.124 --> 00:40:44.193
and everything else will flow from that.

857
00:40:44.193 --> 00:40:45.829
<v Voiceover>So angels aren't looking</v>

858
00:40:45.829 --> 00:40:48.131
for praise or adoration.

859
00:40:48.131 --> 00:40:50.300
Some remarkable insights on this subject

860
00:40:50.300 --> 00:40:52.302
are offered by Betty Eadie

861
00:40:52.302 --> 00:40:54.037
whose book, Embraced by The Light,

862
00:40:54.037 --> 00:40:56.039
is a best-seller.

863
00:40:56.039 --> 00:40:57.693
Betty wrote the book following

864
00:40:57.693 --> 00:40:59.908
an extensive near death experience

865
00:40:59.908 --> 00:41:01.967
where she picked up some definite opinions

866
00:41:01.967 --> 00:41:05.875
about an angel's place in human affairs.

867
00:41:05.875 --> 00:41:09.318
<v ->But don't focus on angels.</v>

868
00:41:09.318 --> 00:41:10.886
If you focus on angels

869
00:41:10.886 --> 00:41:14.289
you are short changing yourself.

870
00:41:14.289 --> 00:41:15.891
Many people have come up to me

871
00:41:15.891 --> 00:41:17.493
and they said, Betty I wanna learn how to

872
00:41:17.493 --> 00:41:20.109
get in contact with my angels.

873
00:41:20.109 --> 00:41:21.563
Why?

874
00:41:21.563 --> 00:41:25.630
Why do you want to learn who the messenger is?

875
00:41:28.470 --> 00:41:31.073
Learn who God is.

876
00:41:31.073 --> 00:41:33.408
I don't even know who my angels are.

877
00:41:33.408 --> 00:41:35.344
I don't remember their names.

878
00:41:35.344 --> 00:41:38.047
I don't try to know what their names are,

879
00:41:38.047 --> 00:41:40.549
I just know that they're there.

880
00:41:40.549 --> 00:41:43.886
I want my relationship to be pure

881
00:41:43.886 --> 00:41:46.422
and anything that you put between you

882
00:41:46.422 --> 00:41:48.791
and God

883
00:41:48.791 --> 00:41:52.928
will put a distance, a space.

884
00:41:52.928 --> 00:41:55.998
Don't put angels there.

885
00:41:55.998 --> 00:42:00.335
<v Voiceover>So again, angels seem to be God's messengers</v>

886
00:42:00.335 --> 00:42:03.239
a link, offered between heaven and earth,

887
00:42:03.239 --> 00:42:06.574
as they've always been.

888
00:42:08.824 --> 00:42:11.447
As in the great stories of the past,

889
00:42:11.447 --> 00:42:14.082
many believe that angels continue to play

890
00:42:14.082 --> 00:42:17.319
an important role in our world's unfolding.

891
00:42:17.319 --> 00:42:19.788
<v ->Chances are that there are members of</v>

892
00:42:19.788 --> 00:42:21.523
your immediate family circle who

893
00:42:21.523 --> 00:42:23.359
have had these experiences,

894
00:42:23.359 --> 00:42:26.485
friends, undoubtedly people at the work place

895
00:42:26.485 --> 00:42:29.164
if you have-- at all

896
00:42:29.164 --> 00:42:30.536
but they're out there, you just don't know it.

897
00:42:30.536 --> 00:42:33.569
Because people are reluctant to

898
00:42:33.569 --> 00:42:35.504
to tell these stories out in public

899
00:42:35.504 --> 00:42:36.639
for fear of ridicule.

900
00:42:36.639 --> 00:42:39.442
<v ->Now we're opening up to an era</v>

901
00:42:39.442 --> 00:42:41.877
where potentially we won't

902
00:42:41.877 --> 00:42:44.744
have to depend on the belief,

903
00:42:44.744 --> 00:42:47.724
disbelief thing anymore.

904
00:42:47.724 --> 00:42:50.522
That now we can talk openly

905
00:42:50.522 --> 00:42:53.002
about our spiritual experiences.

906
00:42:53.002 --> 00:42:55.091
<v ->It helped me a great deal, talking to other people</v>

907
00:42:55.091 --> 00:42:58.026
and share with them what had happened to us

908
00:42:58.026 --> 00:43:01.096
and they would say, it's all right,

909
00:43:01.096 --> 00:43:05.334
we've had a similar experience, you're not crazy.

910
00:43:05.334 --> 00:43:08.070
<v ->I can remember how I felt</v>

911
00:43:08.070 --> 00:43:10.840
when I first began to seriously entertain the idea that

912
00:43:10.840 --> 00:43:13.543
a spiritual realm exists.

913
00:43:13.543 --> 00:43:14.844
Because I had been an agnostic,

914
00:43:14.844 --> 00:43:16.412
I thought the physical was all there was,

915
00:43:16.412 --> 00:43:18.947
I thought the universe was just a big, cold, dead,

916
00:43:18.947 --> 00:43:21.216
random machine that came into being by accident

917
00:43:21.216 --> 00:43:22.318
and we're just little cogs

918
00:43:22.318 --> 00:43:24.153
and it doesn't make any difference what happens

919
00:43:24.153 --> 00:43:26.722
what we do, you know we're here for a few

920
00:43:26.722 --> 00:43:28.156
brief moments on the stage

921
00:43:28.156 --> 00:43:31.193
and then we make our exit into oblivion.

922
00:43:31.193 --> 00:43:34.496
And suddenly I began coming across circumstantial evidence

923
00:43:34.496 --> 00:43:37.433
not scientific proof, but circumstantial evidence

924
00:43:37.433 --> 00:43:38.958
that that was not the case.

925
00:43:38.958 --> 00:43:40.936
That we live in a universe of purpose

926
00:43:40.936 --> 00:43:42.691
a universe of intelligence

927
00:43:42.691 --> 00:43:44.806
and a universe that seems, appears to have been planned

928
00:43:44.806 --> 00:43:46.541
by an unseen hand.

929
00:43:46.541 --> 00:43:49.578
This is more than just a subject to dwell on

930
00:43:49.578 --> 00:43:54.310
and pass on because if this is true

931
00:43:54.310 --> 00:43:56.964
if angels really do exist then a spiritual realm exists

932
00:43:56.964 --> 00:43:58.564
and we have a purpose and a plan

933
00:43:58.564 --> 00:44:00.793
that says something to us.

934
00:44:00.793 --> 00:44:03.358
<v ->Faith.</v>

935
00:44:03.358 --> 00:44:07.229
That all sums it up, without that

936
00:44:07.229 --> 00:44:09.632
you can't get anywhere.

937
00:44:09.632 --> 00:44:13.369
<v ->Being able to yield myself</v>

938
00:44:13.369 --> 00:44:17.206
to the governing of God

939
00:44:17.206 --> 00:44:21.677
is the empowerment that an angelic presence gives to me.

940
00:44:21.677 --> 00:44:25.881
To be able to believe that God is so concerned about

941
00:44:25.881 --> 00:44:29.585
me and you and all of us

942
00:44:29.585 --> 00:44:33.222
that God comes presently into each of our lives

943
00:44:33.222 --> 00:44:36.859
and if we're open enough to receive that presence

944
00:44:36.859 --> 00:44:39.962
then we become so much more open to each other.

945
00:44:39.962 --> 00:44:42.164
And it's that angelic presence that binds us

946
00:44:42.164 --> 00:44:45.434
into one another's lives and we're whole

947
00:44:45.434 --> 00:44:48.036
and at peace.

948
00:44:48.036 --> 00:44:49.338
<v Voiceover>And might the angels'</v>

949
00:44:49.338 --> 00:44:52.608
final and finest message be

950
00:44:52.608 --> 00:44:55.844
you are not alone.

951
00:44:55.844 --> 00:44:58.014
No matter where you travel

952
00:44:58.014 --> 00:45:01.000
or where you end your days,

953
00:45:01.000 --> 00:45:05.654
Could it be that an angel hovers ever near?

954
00:45:05.654 --> 00:45:08.390
Ever offering the great peace

955
00:45:08.390 --> 00:45:11.393
that comes with believing.

956
00:45:11.393 --> 00:45:15.513
(ethereal music)